task_details.mathematical_formulation:
Minimize: 
W = \sum_{i} V_i \times \rho_i 
Cost = \sum_{i} V_i \times \text{Cost/kg}_i 
Subject to: 
\sigma \leq \frac{\sigma_{max}}{\text{SF}} 
\sum_{i} V_i \times \rho_i \leq \text{max_material_usage} 
Where: 
V_i = \text{Volume of member }i 
\rho_i = \text{Density of material }i 
\sigma = \text{Stress on member} 
\sigma_{max} = \text{Maximum stress capacity of material} 
\text{SF} = \text{Safety Factor}

